summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 74E, page 176 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Portions of Lots A, B, C and D, Block 98, Sturtevant's Rainier Beach Lake Park Cottage Tracts; and Portions of Lots 3, 4 and 5, Block 98, Rainier Beach Add.
